OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fperhaps heavy with thunder, lingering
OL,7,Finto the evening but soon fading.
OL,8,FBecoming dry overnight, with prolonged
OL,9,Fclear spells. Turning chilly, with
OL,10,Fsome frost mainly in prone rural
OL,11,Fspots. Some isolated mist and fog
OL,12,Fpatches. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA bright, chilly start, but
OL,15,Fcloud thickening from the west.
OL,16,FOutbreaks of light rain, mainly for
OL,17,Fwestern areas, during the afternoon.
OL,18,FSome brightness lingering in the east.
OL,19,FTurning breezy. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
